::DarkMouse::

Holding onto Quickstrike, she looks at Decadel. "Hi, I'm DarkMouse."
She looked up at Quickstrike and then down at her feet. "I..ah..I'm 
heading to my new quarters." she gave him a small smile.  She was 
still shaking and still needed to talk to Black Aracnia about it all.
